Package: DSADMM
Type: Package
Title: Double-Splitting ADMM for Penalized Rank Regression
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yifan", "Jiang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "yifanjiang767@gmail.com")
    )
Author: Yifan Jiang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yifan Jiang <yifanjiang767@gmail.com>
Description: Implements double-splitting ADMM estimators for high-dimensional
    rank regression with L1 and SCAD penalties. The package code is organized
    from the rank-ADMM simulation scripts used for Example 1 / Table 1 and
    Example 2 / Table 2, preserving their ADMM settings and HBIC tuning
    workflow.
